{"tid":429601,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"［ViuTV］廣告的深度","createTime":"2017-10-09T05:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T17:04:20.000Z","uid":27038,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4f19d32f09bd3d6558a426705ec8d024c0e3c4a2","tid":429601,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:13:51.000Z","msg":"唔係節目，只不過，<br />\n中秋個廣告竟然無人提？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廣告入面運用左月亮同太陽的關係，<br />\n表達出人與人之間的感情，<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/09/130611_54612e352f1b339091b33fd05ca6410d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F09%2F130611_54612e352f1b339091b33fd05ca6410d.jpg&h=7c0d30da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亦都用上左我地細細個就知嘅知識，<br />\n月亮俾地球擋住無得反映太陽光而黑沈沈<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/09/130611_6cec07464b9d46b1db1dba98c4ca0718.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F09%2F130611_6cec07464b9d46b1db1dba98c4ca0718.jpg&h=08a113ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但慢慢咁太陽就照到月亮了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/09/130952_d3fd675fdfc8b19439568762b2b2a985.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F09%2F130952_d3fd675fdfc8b19439568762b2b2a985.jpg&h=8cc1ff9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到最後，仲於到左月圓之夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成個廣告創意加上知識，絕對係一個有深度嘅廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以下大家一齊睇多次啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zxKULk8kvv8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzxKULk8kvv8&d=YCODDMybYN7foeKrmTtIoQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=6e8cf1b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zxKULk8kvv8</a>"},{"pid":"9e92489298928edd19697f42d8b7e65ba4c7e045","tid":429601,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:16:31.000Z","msg":"呀！仲有，首歌聽落好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b9283d77267e9a632174780a3cc3dad0dbf722","tid":429601,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:19:33.000Z","msg":"有啲twist 得濟"},{"pid":"d8e8b11f4e149a63126e961f8a1b2aea537f9446","tid":429601,"uid":27038,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:25:53.000Z","msg":"總好過呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/09/132434_673d583033d2023448d172c755cb381a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F09%2F132434_673d583033d2023448d172c755cb381a.jpg&h=87379599&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開始覺得畫面好靚好唯美，但家下越睇越煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2be8ea337dda2df403d1fbd7242761f0494c11","tid":429601,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T18:24:41.000Z","msg":"